descriptionHtml:
Nothing too unique, just night sky textures I created for myself and chose to share here. The textures for the nebula or galaxy are NOT HIGH QUALITY, so if you are very picky about such things then this mod is probably not for you.

To install the mod just drag and drop the contents of the file into your Skyrim/data folder and merge folders when prompted.

I'd like to give credit to Bethesda games, as always, for Skyrim; also to all of the other night sky mods out there which gave me the inspiration to create my own.

If you like the mod, please feel free to endorse it.
